<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَدَابَةٌ فِي وُجُوهِ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ لَهَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَسْمٌ مِنْ النُّورِ وَالْكُفَّارِ بِالْقَتَرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَخَلْفُهَا الْفِتْنَةُ الدَّجَالُ قَبْلَهُمَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَوْ بَعْدَ قَدْ وَرَدَ الْقَوْلانِ فِي الْخَبَرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَكَمْ خَرَابٍ وَكَمْ خَسْفٍ وَزَلْزَلَةٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَفِيحِ نَارِ وَآيَاتٍ مِنَ النُّذُرِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَنَفْخَةٌ تُذْهِبُ الأَرْوَاحَ شِدَّتُهَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>إِلا الَّذِينَ عَنُوا فِي سُورَةِ الزُّمَرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَأَرْبَعُونَ مِنَ الأَعْوَامِ قَدْ حُسِبْتَ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>لِكَيْ تُبَثَّ بِهَا الأَرْوَاحُ فِي الصُّوَرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>قَامُوا حُفَاةً عُرَاةٌ مِثْلَ مَا خُلِّقُوا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مِنْ هَوْلِ مَا عَايَنُوا سَكْرَى بِلا سُكُرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>قَوْمٌ مُشَاةٌ وَرُكْبَانٌ عَلَى نُجُبِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عَلَيْهِمَا حُلَلٍ أَبْهَى مِنَ الزَّهْرِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَيُسْحَبُ الظَّالِمُونَ الْكَافِرُونَ عَلَى<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وُجُوهِهِمْ وَتُحِيطُ النَّارُ بِالشَّرَرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَالشَّمْسُ قَدْ أُدْنِيَتْ وَالنَّاسُ فِي عَرَقٍ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَفِي زِحَامٍ وَفِي كَرْبٍ وَفِي حَصَرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَالأَرْضُ قَدْ بُدِّلَتْ بَيْضَاءَ لَيْسَ لَهَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>مَخْفَى وَلا مَلْجَأٌ يَبْدُو لِمُسْتَتِرِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>